S&P Mila 40 Index to Include Colombian, Peruvian, Chilean Stocks

-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 
2011-08-29T14:48:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-29/s-p-mila-40-index-to-include-colombian-peruvian-chilean-stocks.html
Colombian, Chilean and Peruvian
bourses announced a new index that will follow the 40 most
liquid companies in the first stock market integration in  Latin
America .  The S&P Mila 40 Index will include 22 Chilean, 6 Peruvian
and 12 Colombian companies, according to a joint e-mailed
statement released today by the securities exchange operators of
the three Andean nations.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blake Schmidt in Bogota at 
 bschmidt16@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at  papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  